data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 1 bathroom home in the heart of Northlake. This move-in ready Cape Code is the perfect place to call home. The main floor features a spacious living room/dinning room, with hardwood floors and recessed lighting. The updated kitchen has great cabinet space and counter top space. The kitchen features butcher block counter tops, a farmers sink, and modern appliances. The main floor also features a laundry room, full bathroom and 1 bedroom. Upstairs you will find 2 additional spacious bedrooms. The spacious backyard is perfect for entertaining and enjoying the seasons with your family in the beautiful covered concrete patio. No other patio like it. Perfect for cookouts or family gatherings. Yard also has additional storage sheds and fire pit. The driveway offers plenty of parking and leads to your a 1 car garage. Prime location located across the street from parks, Grant Park Recreation Center, fields, walking paths, near restaurants, shopping, Wal-mart, Sams, Home Depot, I-290/I-294 expressways, 15 minutes form O'Hare Airport and so much more. A Must See!
